1962;;Five Finger Exercise;;American;;Daniel Mann;;Rosalind Russell, Jack Hawkins;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Five_Finger_Exercise;;It follows a few days in the lives of the Harringtons, who are at war. While the husband and wife fight each other, the son and daughter are on the same path. Then, when a music teacher comes in, things begin to change, until other things start to threaten the peace.